@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kvpipx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v0 + 0.93 / v0 + 0.23)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos((0.13 * 0.38))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.27)))
    tmp = (v2 / wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.33)
    data[tid] = v0
